    <step order="2">Create `src/client/pcf/VisualHost/control/components/CardChrome.tsx`. Props per FR-VH-05. Render a vertical flex stack: header row (title left + corner icons right) + `{children}`. Header uses `tokens.spacingHorizontal*` and `tokens.colorNeutralBackground1` style for divider/elevation as appropriate. Expand button = Fluent v9 `Button appearance="subtle"` + `ArrowMaximize20Regular`.</step>
